setDetails.setDescription: The CMI Index is a digital asset index designed to track performance of  the crypto crypto market. The index is equally weighted between three assets: WBTC, ETH, USDC. The CMI Index allows you to get the profitability of the all crypto market just HODLing only one token.
setDetails.managerDescription: The NFT Index by https://nftindex.tech/ is a digital asset index designed to track tokens performance within the NFT industry.
